data.description: 2.875%  VA Assumabale!! Welcome Home! To this beautiful home on a quiet cul-de-sac with a fabulous lot that backs up to a pond! Located in The Oaks of Cane Bay Plantation, convenient to the YMCA, schools, shopping, dining, and amenities!! With miles of walking/ jogging trails! Entering through the charming front porch, you are greeted by a large foyer, LVP flooring, a tray ceilinged dining room and an office space with french doors. The floor plan offers an open concept with a drop zone, butlers pantry and plenty of storage. The kitchen is perfect for entertaining and connects directly to the dining and living areas. It boasts a gas range, stainless steel appliances, wine rack, granite countertops and a large island. Don't miss the HUGE owners suite located on the first floor.The owners suite offers LVP floors, dual vanity sinks and pond views. Upstairs, you'll find a loft, four spare bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms!  Enjoy your days out front on your welcoming porch or watch the sunset on the back patio overlooking the beautiful pond. The Oaks at Cane Bay has so much to offer you, from walking and jogging trails to the YMCA, restaurants, shopping, Starbucks, Publix and more. Don't miss out on could be the perfect home for you!
